nodes.statement:
For any \(M>0\) and \(\varepsilon>0\):
  \begin{itemize}
    \item[(a)]
      \(\#\bigcup_{m>M,\,m\,\text{sqf}}\{f\in U_m^{(s)} : H(f)<X\}
      = O_\varepsilon(X^{n(n+1)/2+\varepsilon}/M)
      + O(X^{n(n+1)/2-1});\)
    \item[(b)]
      \(\#\bigcup_{m>M,\,m\,\text{sqf}}\{f\in U_m^{(w)} : H(f)<X\}
      = O_\varepsilon(X^{n(n+1)/2+\varepsilon}/M)
      + O_\varepsilon(X^{n(n+1)/2-1/5+\varepsilon}).\)
  \end{itemize}
